 Former Presidential aide, Reno Omokri has stated that men should not hit a woman even when provoked.  The controversial figure stated that individuals should desist from slapping anyone and advised men never to return a slap because men’s skin was created tougher than the ladies to take a slap. In his words: “Dear men, Nobody should EVER slap anyone. But even if a woman slaps you, NEVER slap her back. Leave the room. Don’t be provoked. One of the reasons why God made your facial skin tougher than a woman’s own is so that you can take a woman’s slap without retaliating! It is a very ungentlemanly thing to do. And even Christ taught this: “If anyone slaps you on the right cheek, turn to them the other cheek also.’-Matthew 5:39  Source By ‎Reuben Abati Lucy Muthoni Kibaki was buried yesterday, 9.12 am, Nigerian time, in Othaya, Njeri County, Kenya in the presence of about 300 guests and family members, after a requiem mass attended by over 3,000 dignitaries and 20,000 mourners. She was the wife of President Mwai Kibaki, the third… In "Opinion" A former Presidential adviser, Reno Omokri has warned people against giving birth to children when they do not have a steady source of income. Taking to Twitter, Reno Omokri stated God’s only impact is providing the child with parents, it is left to the parent to provide for the needs… In "Features" The start of the impunity is what remains confusing. Where do we begin?Is it the video of the ladies where they make a false allegation? Is it the bounty that popular musician David Adélékè “Davido”, placed on the heads of the ladies illegally for information leading to them? Is it… In "Entertainment"